-- ds.h1: What is fastn?

`fastn` is a full-stack framework which helps to create web applications. fastn
compiles `.ftd` files to HTML/CSS/JS which can be deployed on your server.

-- ds.h2: Why fastn?

- Easy to learn
- Rich component library
- Opinionated Design System
